ZH: 这个花园里有很多害虫。
EN: There are many pests in this garden.

ZH: 害虫会危害庄稼的生长。
EN: Pests can damage the growth of crops.

ZH: 农民们需要及时进行害虫防治。
EN: Farmers need to control pests in a timely manner.

ZH: 害虫会传播疾病。
EN: Pests can spread diseases.

ZH: 我们需要找到有效的方法来消灭害虫。
EN: We need to find effective ways to eliminate pests.

ZH: 控制害虫的最好方式是定期喷洒农药。
EN: The best way to control pests is to spray pesticides regularly.

ZH: 害虫在夜晚活动得更加频繁。
EN: Pests are more active at night.

ZH: 害虫对庄稼造成了重大损害。
EN: Pests have caused significant damage to crops.

ZH: 害虫数量过多会影响作物的产量。
EN: An excessive number of pests can affect crop yields.

ZH: 害虫会侵害果树。
EN: Pests can infest fruit trees.

ZH: 冬季是控制害虫的好时机。
EN: Winter is a good time to control pests.

ZH: 好的防治措施可以减少害虫的数量。
EN: Good control measures can reduce the number of pests.

ZH: 种植耐寒的庄稼可以减少害虫的侵害。
EN: Planting cold-resistant crops can reduce pest infestations.

ZH: 这个草坪上有很多害虫。
EN: There are many pests on this lawn.

ZH: 小心害虫会影响庄稼的质量。
EN: Be careful, pests can affect the quality of crops.

ZH: 选用有害虫抗性的品种是一个好办法。
EN: Choosing pest-resistant varieties is a good way to deal with pests.

ZH: 害虫数量的爆发会给庄稼带来危害。
EN: An outbreak of pests can be harmful to crops.

ZH: 害虫是作物生长的障碍。
EN: Pests are obstacles to crop growth.

ZH: 使用化学农药可以控制害虫。
EN: Chemical pesticides can control pests.

ZH: 害虫的出现会影响农民的收入。
EN: The appearance of pests can affect farmers' income.
